editorial.title: Lisbon
content: Located in Lisbon, Tagus Marina - Houseboat is in the city center and near the boardwalk. Camoes Theater and Pavilhao do Conhecimento- Ciencia Viva are cultural highlights, and some of the area's notable landmarks include Castle of São Jorge and Lisbon Cathedral. Don't miss out on a visit to Lisbon Oceanarium. Take an opportunity to explore the area for outdoor excitement like ecotours and other activities like segway rentals/tours.

content.text: Just 3.1 mi (5 km) from the airport, Tagus Marina - Houseboat features a marina and puts you within a 15-minute drive of Rossio Square and Avenida da Liberdade. Free WiFi is an added perk, and guests looking to stay active can check out the nearby segway rentals/tours. Also, this houseboat is 0.4 mi (0.7 km) from Lisbon Oceanarium and 5 mi (8.1 km) from Castle of São Jorge. Fellow travelers like the location.

content.text: You'll be asked to pay the following charges by the property at check-in or check-out:
• A tax is imposed by the city: EUR 2.00 per person, per night, up to 7 nights. This tax does not apply to children under 13 years of age.
• Continental breakfast is offered for an extra charge of approximately EUR 10.50 for adults and EUR 8 for children
• Cribs/infant beds are available for EUR 25.0 per night

This property advises that enhanced cleaning and guest safety measures are currently in place.

The property is professionally cleaned; disinfectant is used to clean the property; commonly-touched surfaces are cleaned with disinfectant between stays; bed sheets and towels are laundered at a temperature of at least 60°C/140°F.

Each guestroom is kept vacant for a minimum of 24 hours between bookings.

This property affirms that it follows the cleaning and disinfection practices of Clean & Safe (Portugal).
